name: Penguin (Batman Returns)
description:
This TI is based off the Penguin in the Batman Returns movie. Played by Danny DeVito. This was a tough one to do, since there are not that many great photos out there. But I was able to get about 14 images to create this one here. Doing a couple of runs I think it turned out pretty interesting.

If you have any other suggestions let me know.
